<p>Tip for Reading Files using <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">with</code></p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code># Bad example

f = open('some.txt')
text = f.read()
for line in text.split('\n'):
    print(line)
f.close()

# Better example

with open('some.txt') as f:
    for line in f:
        print(line)    
</code></pre></div></div>

